[5.319247, "o", "\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m __tests__/commands/start.test.ts \u001b[2m(\u001b[22m\u001b[2m44 tests\u001b[22m\u001b[2m)\u001b[22m\u001b[33m 389\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mincludes workflow examples in start help\u001b[32m 5\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses single project when no arg given\u001b[32m 20\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses explicit project arg when given\u001b[32m 4\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22merrors when explicit project not found\u001b[32m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22merrors when multiple projects and no arg\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22merrors when no projects configured\u001b[32m 5\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfalls back to managed staging"]
[5.319316, "o", " config when AO_CONFIG_PATH points to a missing file\u001b[32m 96\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreuses existing clone and generates config\u001b[32m 9\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mclones repo via gh when gh auth is available\u001b[32m 11\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfalls back to git clone when gh is unavailable\u001b[32m 86\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses existing config when repo already has agent-orchestrator.yaml\u001b[32m 18\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mresolves correct project when existing config has multiple projects\u001b[32m 10\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfails on clone error with descriptive message\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — local path argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22madds new local-path projects to staging instead of production\u001b"]
[5.319453, "o", "[32m 7\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — local path argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mrepairs an invalid staging symlink before onboarding a local path\u001b[32m 24\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — browser open waits for port\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mcalls waitForPortAndOpen with orchestrator URL and AbortSignal\u001b[32m 4\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — browser open waits for port\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mskips browser open and lifecycle with --no-dashboard --no-orchestrator\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — browser open waits for port\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mskips browser open but still starts lifecycle with --no-dashboard alone\u001b[32m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mshows reused messaging when strategy is reuse and metadata marks the session reused\u001b[32m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfalls back to attach messaging when strategy is reuse but metadata "]
[5.319507, "o", "is missing\u001b[32m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is delete\u001b[32m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is ignore\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is delete-new\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is ignore-new\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is kill-previous\u001b[32m 4\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mstops orchestrator session and dashboard\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mhandles missing orchestrator session gracefully\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2"]
[5.31955, "o", "mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdefaults to NOT purge OpenCode session when stopping orchestrator\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpasses purge flag when stopping orchestrator with --purge-session\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — autoCreateConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mgenerates config with empty notifiers array (no desktop notifier added by default)\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits immediately for non-TTY caller when AO is already running\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits when human caller selects 'quit'\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpath arg already registered + running: opens dashboard without prompting and does not mutate YAML\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpath arg unregis"]
[5.319577, "o", "tered + AO running: registers in global config and spawns orchestrator without showing the menu\u001b[32m 5\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22moffers to add cwd when AO is running and cwd is an unregistered git repo\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits when human caller selects 'open'\u001b[32m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mkills existing process and continues when human caller selects 'restart'\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mstarts lifecycle and completes without error when --no-dashboard is used\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mcreates new orchestrator entry when human caller selects 'new'\u001b[32m 5\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdoes not mutate YAML when non-TTY caller detects already running (path arg)\u001b[32m 5\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b"]
[5.319592, "o", "[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — path-based deduplication in addProjectToConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mskips addProjectToConfig when path arg matches an existing project\u001b[32m 6\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — path-based deduplication in addProjectToConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdeduplicates via addProjectToConfig when path exists under a different name\u001b[32m 7\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — global registry mutations\u001b[2m > \u001b[22madds a project to the global registry and writes behavior to the repo-local config\u001b[32m 7\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — global registry mutations\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mwrites interactive agent overrides to the repo-local config when using the global registry\u001b[32m 5\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
